{"tid":2074421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日籍旅客稱遭無理拖出賓館　向警方索償約16萬元","createTime":"2020-06-22T05:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T23:47:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1485,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":154,"replies":[{"pid":"830d7159795608a81d1e55c7072893502d4ec32e","tid":2074421,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"居於尖沙嘴重慶大廈的一名疑似日本旅客，聲稱於上月下旬深夜時份，遭警方無理拖出賓館，故日前決定入稟區域法院向警方索償近16萬財物損失。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，3男1女的警員於上月25日凌晨3時半，在沒有取得法庭搜查令下闖進申索人Eishin Kura位於重慶大慶一賓館的房間，4警將申索人物品扔出房外後，隨即以不合法的武力拖走他，並離開該處。申索人批判警方行動無理兼違法，需對其造成的損失負責，包括申索人的手提電話、眼鏡及重要資料等。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 頭條"},{"pid":"e170714b6d7ead9911bb36ab18841730e9ebf2e0","tid":2074421,"uid":53062,"like":587,"dislike":3,"score":584,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"這裡是香港<br />\n警察做錯事無須負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955bfd1b84520e3cec42ae3348f89317c7211876","tid":2074421,"uid":85629,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"賊嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b8267347dc8d193607d3232a8de4f5a0c339f6","tid":2074421,"uid":14543,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"有冇日/英版本放上twitter"},{"pid":"8bef29634fe42c4d5653044f094a79b9ab27566b","tid":2074421,"uid":121255,"like":321,"dislike":6,"score":315,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"執法要道歉 天方夜譚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f24bed2eed81ce3a4cbb0e79c67d5ad00aef89","tid":2074421,"uid":252142,"like":56,"dislike":9,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"要警察賠錢？ is it joke??"}